===Adjective===
'''stubborn'''
#refusing to [[move]] or change one's [[opinion]]; [[obstinate]].
#:''He is pretty '''stubborn''' about his political beliefs, so why bother arguing?''
#:''Blood can make a very '''stubborn''' stain on fabrics if not washed properly.''

